fall[fall.length] = '<div class="title">Clock Strikes 10</div><div class="carbon">The Fall of House Lynch</div><div class="title">1</div><div class="text">If Clue 3 has not been found, each investigator teakes 1 horror. Otherwise, resolve 1 of the following:</div><hr/><div><span class="passFail">3A:</span> <span class="flavour">A fiery figure bolts down the hallway towards the bedroom.</span> <span class="text">Place a zombie in Hallway 2 with a fire token on him. When he is removed from play, place the fire token in his room.</span></div><hr/><div><span class="passFail">3B:</span> <span class="flavour">The skinless remains of a man throws open the door of the laboratory.</span> <span class="text">Place a zombie in the foyer. Each investigator then takes 1 horror.</span></div>'
fall[fall.length] = '<div class="title">Clock Strikes 11</div><div class="carbon">The Fall of House Lynch</div><div class="title">2</div><div class="text">If Clue 2 has not been found, each investigator teakes 1 horror. Otherwise, resolve 1 of the following:</div><hr/><div><span class="passFail">2A:</span> <span class="flavour">A madman picks up his axe and runs down the hall..</span> <span class="text">The keeper may move a maniac up to 2 spaces.</span></div><hr/><div><span class="passFail">2B:</span> <span class="flavour">The lights momentarily go out as an explosion of gunfire echoes down the hall.</span> <span class="text">Each investigator in a bedroom space is dealt 2 damage.</span></div>'
